{"tid":1683653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每次打機想退後我都會咁諗","createTime":"2019-10-30T17:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T19:38:13.000Z","uid":213352,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eca2bc027d965cf55f4629121fd37d7edacd170f","tid":1683653,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"每次有煙出 想退果陣我腦海都會出現<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新屋嶺女義士俾人強姦<br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n<br />\n831<br />\n<br />\n101槍殺學生<br />\n<br />\n手足被狗咬仲要用腳禁實佢個頭<br />\n<br />\n女義士被抽水摸屎忽摸波<br />\n<br />\n陳彥霖妹妹...<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n班狗想拉邊個就拉邊個<br />\n<br />\n每次鳩拉幾十、百個人<br />\n<br />\n講句屌你老母 拉<br />\n<br />\n講你老婆俾人屌 拉<br />\n<br />\n今晚入埋屋拉人<br />\n<br />\n我諗起呢d 我就唔會退後<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想叫大家反抗 和理非果d升級 <br />\n<br />\n我只係分享我既諗法..........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對唔住 我講大話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實我都想香港人真係反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"210a6047932e2a75ed2d967e9471d31a3bcb8d8a","tid":1683653,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:19:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5f55e5e6d1b3da41ac1f0ae48f850af25661849","tid":1683653,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"22c371853e85e0b115d66cc8818cc778a427f4a7","tid":1683653,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:21:49.000Z","msg":"係咁意推"},{"pid":"a2d291e6b9b16b33167117c535ac4452d0173d7d","tid":1683653,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"香港人..."},{"pid":"109276edfd3bb1dc4ff7f618c80ba4319ca325eb","tid":1683653,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"香港人..."},{"pid":"dea3871cf31e24bb9c07df3746af2aeadab30f16","t